data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property is located in a serene neighborhood in Jackson, Georgia, and boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms. You'll be captivated by the extended living space, beautiful high ceilings, and hardwood floors as you enter. The spacious master bedroom has elegant vaulted ceilings with a luxurious master bathroom that includes his and her sinks and a large garden tub for relaxation. The walk-in closet is also spacious, providing ample room for your wardrobe.    Step outside to a spacious back patio that's perfect for entertainment or relaxation. This patio is the perfect spot for hosting barbecues and game nights or enjoying a peaceful morning coffee. It's equipped with everything you need, including a cozy wood-burning fireplace, ceiling fan, and television connection.    This home is move-in ready, and available at an incredibly affordable price of only $265,000. It offers 1,716 square feet of living space, located at 526 Cotton Drive, Jackson, GA 30233, and is sure to impress you with its elegance and comfort.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful property.
